<br>
So, it's apparently very easy for someone to sell their account, someone else buy it, then the original person gets it back.<br>
<br>
That is why I would NEVER buy an account...I'd be to scared I'd pay all this money for one, and then the person would take it back....I don't have money to burn for stuff like that.<br>
